FBIS4-21822 "jptot014__l94122" JPRS-TOT-94-014-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 30 March 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Minibus Hits Landmine in Sirnak, Fifteen Killed Minibus Hits Landmine in Sirnak, Fifteen Killed TA3003190994 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 GMT 30 Mar 94 TA3003190994 Ankara TRT Television Network Turkish BFN [Announcer-read report over still of regional map] [Text] Near Sirnak's Idil District, 15 persons, among them nine village guards, were killed when their minibus hit a land mine laid by terrorists. According to information obtained by a TRT correspondent, the incident occurred around 1430 [1130 GMT].
